Anti-crime activist, Yusuf Abramjee, says the same modus operandi is being used. Courtesy#DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Another Johannesburg businessman has been abducted. 30-year-old Hamza Khan was grabbed outside his family's butchery in Fordsburg on Friday. Armed gangs have kidnapped several business people over the past few months. Anti-crime activist, Yusuf Abramjee, says the same modus operandi is being used. Thirty-year-old Hamza Khan was grabbed from outside his family's butchery in Fordsburg yesterday. Armed gangs have kidnapped several business people over the past few months. Courtesy #DStv403 